同时，韩国宣布已准备就部署[[戰區高空防御飛彈|萨德系统]]将与美国方面进行谈判。<ref>{{Cite web|title = China worried over US-South Korea plans to deploy THAAD missile system - The Economic Times|url = http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/defence/china-worried-over-us-south-korea-plans-to-deploy-thaad-missile-system/articleshow/50892130.cms|website = 印度时报|access-date = 2016-02-07|language = en|archive-date = 2020-08-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200820013416/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/defence/china-worried-over-us-south-korea-plans-to-deploy-thaad-missile-system/articleshow/50892130.cms|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Korea says THAAD 'helpful' to security|url = http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2016/01/205_196787.html|website = 韩国时报|access-date = 2016-02-07|language = en|archive-date = 2016-01-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160130213140/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2016/01/205_196787.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>而中国和俄罗斯对此予以强烈反对的态度。<ref>{{Cite web|title = 危害深远！美应停止推动在韩部署“萨德”|url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-02/22/c_1118121685.htm|website = 新华网|access-date = 2016年2月22日|language = zh-cn|archive-date = 2017年3月5日|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170305062844/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-02/22/c_1118121685.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = U.S. hopes for talks with China about possible THAAD move to South Korea|url = http://www.reuters.com/article/us-southkorea-usa-missiledefense-china-idUSKCN0WO2P2|website = 路透社|access-date = 2016年2月23日|language = en|archive-date = 2021年3月13日|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210313100722/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-southkorea-usa-missiledefense-china-idUSKCN0WO2P2|dead-url = no}}</ref>

===中美外长会晤和谈判===
在韩半岛局势愈加紧张的时候，[[中华人民共和国外交部|中国外交部]][[中国外交部长列表|部长]][[王毅|王毅]]于2月24日出访美国与[[美国国务卿|美国国务卿]][[约翰·克里|约翰·克里]]会晤并商讨多項问题<ref>{{Cite web|title = 王毅2016访美首秀：将谈南海、朝核等“敏感议题”|url = http://news.sohu.com/20160223/n438256111.shtml|website = [[搜狐|搜狐]]|access-date = 2016年2月23日|language = zh-cn|archive-date = 2019年6月12日|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190612081307/http://news.sohu.com/20160223/n438256111.shtml|dead-url = no}}</ref>。经过复杂商讨，中美双方就两国扩大对朝鲜制裁的草案达成了一致，并待安理会最终通过。<ref>{{Cite web|title = 中美达成协议〝制裁朝鲜〞金正恩处境雪上加霜|url = http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/gb/2016/02/26/a1254745.html|website = 新唐人|access-date = 2016-02-26|language = zh-hans|archive-date = 2017-03-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170305001436/http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/gb/2016/02/26/a1254745.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==动议==
2月25日，美国向联合国安理会递交了制裁朝鲜决议草案。美国常驻联合国代表[[萨曼莎·鲍尔|萨曼莎·鲍尔]]表示，决议草案将禁止向朝鲜出售小型武器和其它常规武器，限制并在部分情况下彻底禁止朝鲜出口[[煤|煤]]、[[铁|铁]]、[[金|金]]、[[钛|钛]]和稀土矿。鲍尔表示，这项决议若获得通过，将是“20年多来安理会实施的最严厉制裁”。中国驻联合国代表[[刘结一|刘结一]]表示，中方反对所有核试验以及弹道导弹技术的测试，并希望通过此次的决议防止此类事件再次发生。<ref>{{Cite web|title = 美国向安理会递交制裁朝鲜决议|url = http://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%91%E5%AE%89%E7%90%86%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%92%E4%BA%A4%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%9C%9D%E9%B2%9C%E5%86%B3%E8%AE%AE/a-19076421|website = [[德国之声|德国之声]]|access-date = 2016-02-26|language = zh-hans|archive-date = 2016-05-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160502235950/http://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%91%E5%AE%89%E7%90%86%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%92%E4%BA%A4%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%9C%9D%E9%B2%9C%E5%86%B3%E8%AE%AE/a-19076421|dead-url = no}}</ref>俄罗斯常驻联合国副代表彼得·伊里切夫称，俄方需要时间研究该草案，最早可能在3月初进行表决。<ref>{{Cite web|title = 美国向安理会提交制裁朝鲜决议草案|url = http://cn.reuters.com/article/northkorea-nuclear-usa-idCNKCS0VZ05T|website = [[路透社|路透社]]|access-date = 2016-02-26|language = zh-hans|archive-date = 2017-06-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170628214950/http://cn.reuters.com/article/northkorea-nuclear-usa-idCNKCS0VZ05T|dead-url = no}}</ref>

